&lt;p&gt;We are looking for a forward-thinking Pharmacy Technician to join our expanding Primary Care Network team working for the Slough Provider Innovation Network Enterprise (SPINE ) Primary Care Network (PCN).&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The successful candidate will work across 4 practices developing this new role and will be closely supported by the PCN Clinical Director, GPs and PCN Clinical Pharmacist.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The role will suit a forward-thinking, innovative and enthusiastic PharmacyTechnician who is able to work collaboratively across the network. If you are adaptable, self-motivated and organised, and possess the necessary qualities and skills for this post, we look forward to hearing from you.&lt;/p&gt;
